label: AL rdfs:label@en
definition: AL IAO:0000115@en
comment: AL rdfs:comment@en

label: piece of beef
Equivalence axiom: 'piece of cow' and 'has part' some ('derives from' some 'animal muscle tissue cut')
definition: A piece of animal meat that is derived from cow.

label: piece of beef (raw)
definition: A raw piece of beef.

label: piece of beef (boneless)
Equivalence axiom: 'piece of beef' and not ('has part' some ('derives from' some 'bone element'))
definition: A piece of boneless beef.

label: piece of beef (cubed)
definition: A piece of boneless beef that has a cubic shape.
comment: Cubed meat should be free from bones, cartilage, lymph glands, and most or all connective tissue and fat.

label: piece of beef (cubed, raw)
definition: A raw cubic piece of beef.

label: piece of beef (with bone)
Equivalence axiom: 'piece of beef' and 'has part' some ('derives from' some 'bone element')
definition: A piece of beef that contains bone material.

label: piece of beef (with bone, raw)
Equivalence axiom: 'piece of beef (with bone)' and 'has quality' some 'raw'
definition: A raw piece of beef that contains bone material.

label: piece of beef (deboned)
definition: A piece of deboned beef.

label: piece of beef (mechanically deboned)
definition: A piece of beef that is mechanically deboned by forcing bones, with attached edible meat, under high pressure through a sieve or similar device to separate the bone from the edible meat tissue.

label: piece of beef (mechanically deboned, raw)
Equivalence axiom: 'piece of beef (mechanically deboned)' and 'has quality' some 'raw'
definition: A raw piece of mechanically deboned beef.

label: piece(s) of beef
Equivalence axiom: 'has member' some 'piece of beef' and 'has member' only 'piece of beef'
definition: One or more pieces of beef.

label: piece(s) of beef (raw)
definition: One or more raw pieces of beef.

label: piece(s) of beef (boneless)
Equivalence axiom: 'piece(s) of beef' and not ('has part' some ('derives from' some 'bone element'))
definition: One or more pieces of boneless beef.

label: beef (ground)
definition: Beef that has been ground.

label: beef (ground, raw)
definition: Raw beef that has been ground.

label: piece(s) of beef (deboned)
definition: One or more pieces of deboned beef.

label: piece(s) of beef (deboned, raw)
definition: One or more raw pieces of deboned beef.

label: piece(s) of beef (mechanically deboned)
definition: One or more pieces of mechanically deboned beef.

label: piece(s) of beef (mechanically deboned, raw)
Equivalence axiom: 'piece(s) of beef (mechanically deboned)' and 'has quality' some 'raw'
definition: One or more raw pieces of mechanically deboned beef.

label: piece(s) of beef (frozen)
definition: One or more pieces of frozen beef.

label: beef (ground, fresh frozen)
definition: Beef that has been ground and is fresh frozen.

label: beef (minced)
definition: Beef that has been minced with a blade.

label: beef (ground, lean)
definition: Beef that is ground and lean.

label: beef (ground, extra lean)
definition: Beef that is ground and extra lean.

label: beef (ground, medium)
definition: Beef that is medium ground.

label: beef (ground, regular)
definition: Beef that is ground and regular.

label: beef (ground, sirloin)
definition: Beef that comes from sirloin region and is ground.

label: butchery cut of beef
definition: A butchery cut of beef that is primal, sub-primal or a retail cut.

label: butchery cut of beef (raw)
definition: A raw butchery cut of beef.

label: beef primal cut
definition: A cut of beef that is initially separated from the carcass of a{n} {organism} during butchering.

label: beef sub-primal cut
definition: A smaller cut of beef that is obtained from the larger primal cut of beef.

label: beef retail cut
definition: A cut of beef that is derived from a sub-primal, individual muscle cut or minor primal cut.

label: beef round
definition: A beef cut that comes from the 'round', the rear leg of the beef.
comment: Sometimes referred to as the “Beef Hip.”

label: beef round (raw)
definition: A raw beef round cut.

label: beef bottom round
definition: A beef cut that comes from the outside of the rear leg.
comment: Given the name “Bottom” because anatomically it is located below the Top Round and the Eye of Round in the Round primal.

label: beef bottom round (raw)
definition: A raw beef bottom round cut.

label: beef bottom round steak
Equivalence axiom: 'beef steak' and 'derives from' some 'beef bottom round'
definition: A steak cut from the beef bottom round.
comment: Steak derived from the Bottom Round Flat, also known as an Outside Round.

label: beef bottom round steak (raw)
Equivalence axiom: 'beef bottom round steak' and 'has quality' some 'raw'
definition: A raw beef bottom round steak.

label: beef bottom round steak (boneless)
Equivalence axiom: 'beef bottom round steak' and not ('has part' some ('derives from' some 'bone element'))
definition: A boneless beef bottom round steak.

label: beef bottom round steak (boneless, raw)
Equivalence axiom: 'beef bottom round steak (boneless)' and 'has quality' some 'raw'
definition: A raw and boneless beef bottom round steak.

label: beef bottom round roast
Equivalence axiom: 'beef roast' and 'derives from' some 'beef bottom round'
definition: A roast cut from the beef bottom round.
comment: Roast derived from the Bottom Round Flat, also known as an Outside Round.

label: beef bottom round roast (raw)
Equivalence axiom: 'beef bottom round roast' and 'has quality' some 'raw'
definition: A raw beef bottom round roast.

label: beef bottom round roast (boneless)
Equivalence axiom: 'beef bottom round roast' and not ('has part' some ('derives from' some 'bone element'))
definition: A boneless beef bottom round roast.

label: beef bottom round roast (boneless, raw)
Equivalence axiom: 'beef bottom round roast (boneless)' and 'has quality' some 'raw'
definition: A raw and boneless beef bottom round roast.

label: beef top round
definition: A beef cut that comes from the inside of the rear leg.
comment: Given the name “Top” because anatomically it is located directly above the Bottom Round and the Eye of Round in the Round primal.

label: beef top round (raw)
definition: A raw beef top round cut.

label: beef top round steak
Equivalence axiom: 'beef steak' and 'derives from' some 'beef top round'
definition: A steak cut from the beef top round.

label: beef top round steak (raw)
Equivalence axiom: 'beef top round steak' and 'has quality' some 'raw'
definition: A raw beef top round steak.

label: beef top round steak (boneless)
Equivalence axiom: 'beef top round steak' and not ('has part' some ('derives from' some 'bone element'))
definition: A boneless beef top round steak.

label: beef top round steak (boneless, raw)
Equivalence axiom: 'beef top round steak (boneless)' and 'has quality' some 'raw'
definition: A raw and boneless beef top round steak.

label: beef top round steak (cap off)
definition: A beef top round steak in which the top cap portion has been separated off.

label: beef top round steak (cap off, raw)
Equivalence axiom: 'beef top round steak (cap off)' and 'has quality' some 'raw'
definition: A raw beef top round steak in which the top cap portion has been separated off.

label: beef top round steak (cap off, boneless, raw)
Equivalence axiom: 'beef top round steak (cap off)' and 'beef top round steak (boneless)' and 'has quality' some 'raw'
definition: A raw and boneless beef top round steak in which the top cap portion has been separated off.

label: beef top round roast
Equivalence axiom: 'beef roast' and 'derives from' some 'beef top round'
definition: A roast cut from the beef top round.

label: beef top round roast (raw)
Equivalence axiom: 'beef top round roast' and 'has quality' some 'raw'
definition: A raw beef top round roast.

label: beef top round roast (boneless)
Equivalence axiom: 'beef top round roast' and not ('has part' some ('derives from' some 'bone element'))
definition: A boneless beef top round roast.

label: beef top round roast (boneless, raw)
Equivalence axiom: 'beef top round roast (boneless)' and 'has quality' some 'raw'
definition: A raw and boneless beef top round roast.

label: beef sirloin tip
definition: A beef cut that comes from the round primal, and is found on the front end of the rear leg.
comment: Given the name “Sirloin Tip” because anatomically it is located next to the tip of the Sirloin.

label: beef sirloin tip (raw)
definition: A raw beef sirloin tip cut.

label: beef sirloin tip roast
definition: A roast cut from the beef sirloin tip.

label: beef sirloin tip roast (raw)
Equivalence axiom: 'beef sirloin tip roast' and 'has quality' some 'raw'
definition: A raw beef sirloin tip roast.

label: beef sirloin tip steak
definition: A steak cut from the beef sirloin tip.

label: beef sirloin tip steak (raw)
Equivalence axiom: 'beef sirloin tip steak' and 'has quality' some 'raw'
definition: A raw beef sirloin tip steak.

label: beef sirloin tip side roast
definition: A roast that derives from beef sirloin tip and only consists of M.vastus lateralis.

label: beef sirloin tip side roast (raw)
Equivalence axiom: 'beef sirloin tip side roast' and 'has quality' some 'raw'
definition: A raw beef sirloin tip side roast.

label: beef sirloin tip side steak
Equivalence axiom: 'beef steak' and 'derives from' some 'beef sirloin tip side roast'
definition: A steak cut from the beef sirloin tip side roast.

label: beef sirloin tip side steak (raw)
Equivalence axiom: 'beef sirloin tip side steak' and 'has quality' some 'raw'
definition: A raw beef sirloin tip side steak.

label: beef sirloin tip center roast
definition: A roast that derives from beef sirloin tip and only consists of M.rectus femoris.

label: beef sirloin tip center roast (raw)
Equivalence axiom: 'beef sirloin tip center roast' and 'has quality' some 'raw'
definition: A raw beef sirloin tip center roast.

label: beef sirloin tip center steak
Equivalence axiom: 'beef steak' and 'derives from' some 'beef sirloin tip center roast'
definition: A steak cut from the beef sirloin tip center roast.

label: beef sirloin tip center steak (raw)
Equivalence axiom: 'beef sirloin tip center steak' and 'has quality' some 'raw'
definition: A raw beef sirloin tip center steak.

label: beef eye of round
definition: A beef cut that is an elongated muscle located in the center of the beef round cut, and thus is named “Eye.”
comment: This extremely lean cut is shaped similar to a Tenderloin, but is much less tender.

label: beef eye of round (raw)
Equivalence axiom: 'beef eye of round' and 'has quality' some 'raw'
definition: A raw beef eye of round cut.

label: beef eye of round roast
Equivalence axiom: 'beef roast' and 'derives from' some 'beef eye of round'
definition: A roast cut from the beef eye of round.

label: beef eye of round roast (raw)
Equivalence axiom: 'beef eye of round roast' and 'has quality' some 'raw'
definition: A raw beef eye of round roast.

label: beef eye of round steak
Equivalence axiom: 'beef steak' and 'derives from' some 'beef eye of round'
definition: A steak cut from the beef eye of round.

label: beef eye of round steak (raw)
Equivalence axiom: 'beef eye of round steak' and 'has quality' some 'raw'
definition: A raw beef eye of round steak.

label: beef chuck
definition: A beef cut that extends from the neck to the fifth rib and includes the shoulder blade and upper arm.

label: beef chuck (raw)
definition: A raw beef chuck cut.

label: beef chuck tender
definition: A beef cut that consists of M. supraspinatus which lies dorsal to the medial ridge of the blade bone.
comment: The name comes from its shape which is long and narrow with a pointed tip, similar to a Tenderloin.

label: beef chuck tender (raw)
definition: A raw beef chuck tender cut.

label: beef chuck tender steak
definition: A steak cut from the beef chuck tender.

label: beef chuck tender steak (raw)
Equivalence axiom: 'beef chuck tender steak' and 'has quality' some 'raw'
definition: A raw beef chuck tender steak.

label: beef chuck tender roast
definition: A roast cut from the beef chuck tender.
comment: Also referred to as “Mock Tender” Roast because it has a similar appearance to a Tenderloin Roast.
Exact Synonym: beef medallion pot roast|beef mock tender roast

label: beef chuck tender roast (raw)
Equivalence axiom: 'beef chuck tender roast' and 'has quality' some 'raw'
definition: A raw beef chuck tender roast.

label: beef chuck roll
definition: A large, boneless cut that comes from between the ribs and backbone. It contains a mix of tender and somewhat tough muscles, which are fabricated into smaller cuts known as the chuck eye roll and the chuck under blade.
comment: Extension of the Ribeye Roll that remains in the Chuck.

label: beef chuck roll (raw)
definition: A raw beef chuck roll cut.

label: beef chuck eye roll
definition: The top portion of the chuck roll that is separated from the under-blade section.
comment: The top portion of the Chuck Roll that most resembles a Ribeye Roll.

label: beef chuck eye roll (raw)
Equivalence axiom: 'beef chuck eye roll' and 'has quality' some 'raw'
definition: A raw beef chuck eye roll cut.

label: beef chuck eye roast
definition: A roast cut from any portion of the chuck eye roll, typically the center.

label: beef chuck eye roast (raw)
Equivalence axiom: 'beef chuck eye roast' and 'has quality' some 'raw'
definition: A raw beef chuck eye roast.

label: beef chuck eye steak
definition: A steak cut from the rib end only of the chuck eye roll.
Exact Synonym: beef chuck eye roll steak (boneless) | delmonico steak

label: beef chuck eye steak (raw)
Equivalence axiom: 'beef chuck eye steak' and 'has quality' some 'raw'
definition: A raw beef chuck eye steak.

label: beef country-style rib
definition: A cut made by splitting a chuck eye roll in half lengthwise, resulting in two boneless, country-style ribs.
Exact Synonym: boneless country style rib|boneless Chuck roast

label: beef country-style rib (raw)
definition: A raw beef country-style rib.

label: beef under blade
definition: A meat cut that is the flatter portion of the Chuck Roll and is under the Chuck Eye Roll.

label: beef sierra steak
definition: A thin muscle that lays in the seam between the chuck eye roll and under blade.

label: beef sierra steak (raw)
definition: A raw beef sierra steak.

label: beef denver steak
definition: A beef cut from the center of the under blade.
comment: Steaks cut across the grain from the fourth most tender muscle.
Exact Synonym: chuck under blade center steak|chuck under blade steak

label: beef denver steak (raw)
definition: A raw beef denver steak.

label: beef denver roast
definition: A roast cut in which under blade with other muscles and connective tissue are removed and either left whole or portioned.

label: beef denver roast (raw)
definition: A beef denver roast that is raw.

label: beef shoulder clod
definition: A large muscle system which lies dorsal and posterior to the elbow joint, ventral and posterior to the ridge of the scapula (blade bone) and is anterior to the 6th rib.
comment: Centred around the scapula or blade bone in the Chuck. Scapula is removed to make this a boneless subprimal.

label: beef shoulder clod (raw)
definition: A raw beef shoulder clod.

label: beef shoulder clod arm roast
definition: The largest section of the shoulder clod that consist of the large muscle system of the thick end of the shoulder.
comment: Commonly referred to as clod heart. Leave whole or cut into roasts, but remove large connective tissue to assist with tenderness.

label: beef shoulder clod arm roast (raw)
Equivalence axiom: 'beef shoulder clod arm roast' and 'has quality' some 'raw'
definition: A raw beef shoulder clod arm roast.

label: beef shoulder steak
Subclass axiom: 'derives from' some 'beef shoulder clod arm roast'
definition: A steak cut across the grain from the shoulder clod arm roast.
Exact Synonym: beef arm steak|beef arm chuck steak

label: beef shoulder steak (raw)
definition: A raw beef shoulder steak.

label: beef shoulder roast
definition: A roast cut from the beef shoulder clod.

label: beef shoulder roast (raw)
definition: A raw beef shoulder roast.

label: beef ranch steak
Subclass axiom: 'derives from' some 'beef shoulder clod arm roast'
definition: A steak cut across the grain from the shoulder clod arm roast similar to the shoulder steak. Visible connective tissue and associated lean must be removed to qualify as a Ranch Steak.

label: beef ranch steak (raw)
definition: A raw beef ranch steak.

label: beef shoulder petite tender
definition: The smallest muscle of the beef shoulder clod that is shaped like the tenderloin, but is tender and more affordable.

label: beef shoulder petite tender (raw)
Equivalence axiom: 'beef shoulder petite tender' and 'has quality' some 'raw'
definition: A raw beef shoulder petite tender.

label: beef shoulder petite tender medallion
definition: A small tender medallion cut from the beef shoulder petite tender.
comment: Whole shoulder petite tender is sliced end-to-end for portions or medallions.

label: beef shoulder petite tender medallion (raw)
Equivalence axiom: 'beef shoulder petite tender medallion' and 'has quality' some 'raw'
definition: A raw beef shoulder petite tender medallion.

label: beef top blade
definition: The second most tender muscle in the animal that is derived from the shoulder clod.  However, internal connective tissue should be removed to preserve that tenderness.
comment: However, internal connective tissue should be removed to preserve that tenderness.

label: beef top blade (raw)
definition: A raw beef top blade cut.

label: beef top blade steak
definition: A beef steak cut that is end-to-end from the whole top blade.

label: beef top blade steak (raw)
Equivalence axiom: 'beef top blade steak' and 'has quality' some 'raw'
definition: A raw beef top blade steak.

label: beef flat iron steak
definition: A steak cut from the top blade, where the cutting method removes internal connective tissue from the whole Top Blade.

label: beef flat iron steak (raw)
Equivalence axiom: 'beef flat iron steak' and 'has quality' some 'raw'
definition: A raw beef flat iron steak.

label: beef chuck short rib
definition: A cut that is derived from the beef chuck and must include rib 2 through 5.
comment: Can be offered bone-in and/or boneless

label: beef chuck short rib (raw)
Equivalence axiom: 'beef chuck short rib' and 'has quality' some 'raw'
definition: A raw beef chuck short rib.

label: beef chuck short rib (boneless)
definition: A cut from beef chuck short rib that is an individual muscle and is boneless.

label: beef chuck short rib (boneless, raw)
Equivalence axiom: 'beef chuck short rib (boneless)' and 'has quality' some 'raw'
definition: A raw and boneless beef chuck short rib.

label: beef square cut chuck
definition: A beef cut that is the portion of the forequarter after removal of the rib, shortplate, foreshank and brisket.

label: beef square cut chuck (raw)
Equivalence axiom: 'beef square cut chuck' and 'has quality' some 'raw'
definition: A raw beef square cut chuck.

label: beef 7-bone chuck steak
definition: A beef steak cut that is identified by its 7-shaped bone. The 7-bone is made by cutting steaks across the scapula or blade bone.

label: beef 7-bone chuck steak (raw)
definition: A raw beef 7-bone chuck steak.

label: beef 7-bone chuck roast
definition: A beef roast cut that is identified by its 7-shaped bone. The 7-bone is made by cutting roasts across the scapula or blade bone.

label: beef 7-bone chuck roast (raw)
definition: A raw beef 7-bone chuck roast.

label: beef blade chuck steak
definition: A steak cut from the flat bone portion of the blade that comes from ribs 4 through 5.

label: beef blade chuck steak (raw)
Equivalence axiom: 'beef blade chuck steak' and 'has quality' some 'raw'
definition: A raw beef blade chuck steak.

label: beef blade chuck roast
definition: A roast cut from the flat bone portion of the blade that comes from ribs 4 through 5.
Exact Synonym: chuck blade pot roast|chuck roast 1st cut|chuck roast blade cut

label: beef blade chuck roast (raw)
Equivalence axiom: 'beef blade chuck roast' and 'has quality' some 'raw'
definition: A raw beef blade chuck roast.

label: beef chuck roast
definition: A beef roast that comes from the center portion of the Chuck Roll.
comment: It can be called chuck center roast.
Exact Synonym: beef center cut chuck roast|beef chuck center roast|beef chuck pot roast|beef pot roast

label: beef chuck roast (raw)
definition: A raw beef chuck roast.

label: beef chuck steak
definition: A beef steak that comes from the center portion of the Chuck Roll.
comment: It can be called chuck center steak.

label: beef chuck steak (raw)
definition: A raw beef chuck steak.

label: beef cross-rib roast
definition: A beef cut that is adjacent to the arm and includes ribs 2 through 5.

label: beef cross-rib roast (raw)
definition: A raw beef cross-rib roast.

label: beef chuck arm steak
definition: A steak cut from the arm bone (humerus) of the upper forelimb.

label: beef chuck arm steak (raw)
Equivalence axiom: 'beef chuck arm steak' and 'has quality' some 'raw'
definition: A raw beef chuck arm steak.

label: beef chuck arm roast
definition: A roast cut from the arm bone (humerus) of the upper forelimb.

label: beef chuck arm roast (raw)
Equivalence axiom: 'beef chuck arm roast' and 'has quality' some 'raw'
definition: A raw beef chuck arm roast.

label: beef chuck neck roast
definition: A beef cut that is derived from the anterior end of the untrimmed chuck roll.

label: beef chuck neck roast (raw)
Equivalence axiom: 'beef chuck neck roast' and 'has quality' some 'raw'
definition: A raw beef chuck neck roast.

label: beef chuck flap/edge roast
definition: A roast cut is made during fabrication to square off the chuck roll.

label: beef chuck flap/edge roast (raw)
Equivalence axiom: 'beef chuck flap/edge roast' and 'has quality' some 'raw'
definition: A raw beef chuck flap/edge roast.

label: beef loin
definition: A beef primal cut that comes from the area below the backbone .
comment: The area below the backbone is home to some of the most tender and popular cuts of beef, such as the Tenderloin, Strip Steak, T-Bone and Porterhouse Steaks. Loin cuts are exceptionally prepared on the grill or under a broiler.

label: beef loin (raw)
definition: A raw beef loin cut.

label: beef short loin (raw)
definition: A raw beef short loin cut.

label: beef porterhouse steak
definition: A beef steak that is prepared from the beef short loin. The maximum width of the tenderloin must be atleast 1.25 inches (3.2cm) when measured parallel to the length of the backbone.
comment: Differentiated from the T-Bone steak by its larger Tenderloin muscle.
Exact Synonym: beef loin porterhouse steak bone in

label: beef porterhouse steak (raw)
definition: A raw beef porterhouse steak.

label: beef T-bone steak
definition: A beef steak that is prepared from the beef short loin. The maximum width of the tenderloin must be at least 1/2 inch (13mm) when measured parallel to the length of the backbone.
comment: The name originates from the characteristic T-shape of its bone.

label: beef T-bone steak (raw)
definition: A raw beef T-bone steak.

label: beef strip loin (bone-in)
definition: A cut refers to the group of muscles that extends the length of the Top Loin adjacent to the spine bone and on top of the finger bone.

label: beef strip loin (bone-in, raw)
definition: A raw beef strip loin that contains bone.

label: beef strip loin (boneless)
definition: A group of muscles that extends the length of the top loin adjacent to the spine bone and on top of the finger bone.

label: beef strip loin (boneless, raw)
definition: A raw and boneless beef strip loin.

label: beef strip roast (boneless)
definition: A roast cut that comes from boneless beef strip loin.

label: beef strip roast (boneless, raw)
definition: A raw beef strip roast.

label: beef strip steak (boneless)
definition: A cut that comes from the top loin or strip loin into uniform steak.

label: beef strip steak (boneless, raw)
definition: A raw and boneless beef strip steak.

label: beef strip steak (bone-in)
definition: A beef strip steak that contains bone material.

label: beef strip steak (bone-in, raw)
definition: A raw beef strip steak that contains bone material.

label: beef strip petite roast
definition: A smaller roasting option than Strip Roast.
comment: Cut by removing the vein end and splitting the Strip Loin in half, lengthwise.

label: beef strip petite roast (raw)
Equivalence axiom: 'beef strip petite roast' and 'has quality' some 'raw'
definition: A raw beef strip petite roast.

label: beef strip fillet
definition: A thick cut but smaller diameter than beef strip steak.
comment: Commonly cut 1 to 1¼ inch thick.

label: beef strip fillet (raw)
definition: A raw beef strip fillet.

label: beef tenderloin (raw)
definition: A raw beef tenderloin.

label: beef tenderloin (bone-in)
definition: A meat cut that is an inside muscle of the beef loin.

label: beef tenderloin (bone-in, raw)
definition: A raw beef tenderloin that contains bone material.

label: beef tenderloin steak (bone-in)
definition: A raw beef tenderloin steak.

label: beef tenderloin steak (bone-in, raw)
definition: A raw beef tenderloin steak.

label: beef tenderloin (boneless)
definition: A cut that is a long, narrow, and lean muscle located within the loin, and is the most tender cut of beef.

label: beef tenderloin (boneless, raw)
definition: A raw and boneless beef tenderloin.

label: beef tenderloin roast
definition: A roast cut from the larger tenderloin.
Exact Synonym: beef filet mignon roast|chateaubriand tenderloin roast|boneless beef tenderloin roast

label: beef tenderloin roast (raw)
definition: A raw beef tenderloin roast.

label: beef tenderloin steak
definition: A boneless steak cut from the tenderloin.

label: beef tenderloin steak (raw)
definition: A raw beef tenderloin steak.

label: beef sirloin
definition: A beef primal cut that is contained within the larger cut 'beef loin'. It is located between the short loin and the round and includes the hip section and ends at the socket of the pelvis.
comment: Further separated into the Top and Bottom Sirloin Butts.

label: beef sirloin (raw)
definition: A raw beef sirloin cut.

label: beef top sirloin butt
definition: A beef cut that is located behind the beef short loin on the top back end of the animal.
comment: The name originates from its anatomical location on the “Top” (dorsal) of the Sirloin.

label: beef top sirloin butt (raw)
Equivalence axiom: 'beef top sirloin butt' and 'has quality' some 'raw'
definition: A raw beef top sirloin butt.

label: beef top sirloin steak
Equivalence axiom: 'beef steak' and 'derives from' some 'beef top sirloin butt'
definition: A steak cut from the beef top sirloin butt that is flavourful and juicy.
comment: The name originates from its anatomical location on the “Top” (dorsal) of the Sirloin.
Exact Synonym: boneless top sirloin steak|top sirloin butt steak, boneless|top sirloin center-cut steak|top sirloin steak boneless cap off|top sirloin steak cap off

label: beef top sirloin steak (raw)
Equivalence axiom: 'beef top sirloin steak' and 'has quality' some 'raw'
definition: A raw beef top sirloin steak.

label: beef top sirloin roast
definition: A roast cut from the beef top sirloin.

label: beef top sirloin roast (raw)
Equivalence axiom: 'beef top sirloin roast' and 'has quality' some 'raw'
definition: A raw beef top sirloin roast.

label: beef top sirloin petite roast
definition: A roast cut that is a smaller version of the larger {animal top sirloin roast
comment: Roasts are called “Petite” due to their smaller size.

label: beef top sirloin petite roast (raw)
Equivalence axiom: 'beef top sirloin petite roast' and 'has quality' some 'raw'
definition: A raw beef top sirloin petite roast.

label: beef top sirloin fillet
definition: A cut that is portioned from a top sirloin steak.
comment: Filet is a French term meaning a solid piece of meat.

label: beef top sirloin fillet (raw)
Equivalence axiom: 'beef top sirloin fillet' and 'has quality' some 'raw'
definition: A raw beef top sirloin fillet.

label: beef culotte steak
definition: A beef steak cut from the triangle-shaped muscle that caps or covers the top sirloin.

label: beef culotte steak (raw)
definition: A raw beef culotte steak.

label: beef culotte roast
definition: A beef roast cut from the triangle-shaped muscle that caps or covers the top sirloin.

definition: An individual muscle from the picnic of a boneless pork shoulder primal. The cut location is the anterior end of the Pectoralis Profundi adjacent to but before the flat.
comment: It is the fan or point portion of the Pectoralis Profundi thus giving it the name 'point'.

label: pork brisket point (raw)
definition: A raw pork brisket point cut.

label: leaf lard
definition: Lard that is obtained from the "flare" visceral fat deposit surrounding the kidneys and inside the loin of a pig.

label: leaf lard (raw)
definition: Raw leaf lard.

label: pork jowl
definition: A cut of meat from a pig's cheek.

label: pork jowl (raw)
definition: A raw pork jowl.

label: veal leg
definition: A veal cut that is the portion of hindquarter remaining after the removal of loin.

label: veal leg (raw)
definition: A raw veal leg.

label: veal top round
definition: A cut that comes from the inside of the rear leg of a calf.
comment: Given the name “Top” because anatomically it is located directly above the Bottom Round and the Eye of Round in the Round primal.

label: veal top round (raw)
definition: A raw veal top round cut.

label: veal hindshank
definition: A meat cut from the upper part of a hind leg.
comment: URMIS characteristic - Bone in

label: veal hindshank (raw)
definition: A raw veal hindshank cut.

label: veal loin
definition: A veal primal cut that comes from the area below the backbone .

label: veal loin (raw)
definition: A raw veal loin cut.

label: veal rib
definition: A veal primal cut that is situated under the front section of the backbone and used primarily for support.

label: veal rib (raw)
definition: A raw veal rib.

label: veal rib roast
definition: A veal roast that is derived from the rib section.
comment: URMIS characteristics - Bone in

label: veal rib roast (raw)
definition: A raw veal roast.

label: veal breast
definition: A veal primal cut that consist of the plate and brisket portion of the forequarter (intact) and shall contain 11 ribs.
comment: Minor primal

label: veal breast (raw)
definition: A raw veal breast.

label: veal breast (boneless)
Equivalence axiom: 'veal breast' and not ('has part' some ('derives from' some 'bone element'))
definition: A boneless veal breast.

label: veal breast (boneless, raw)
definition: A raw and boneless veal breast.

label: veal foreshank
definition: A veal primal cut that is the foreleg portion from the chuck.
comment: Minor primal.  URMIS characteristic - Bone in

label: veal foreshank (raw)
definition: A raw veal foreshank cut.

label: veal sirloin
definition: A veal primal cut that is contained within the larger primal cut 'veal loin'. It is located between the short loin and the leg (round) and includes the hip section and ends at the socket of the pelvis.

label: veal sirloin (raw)
definition: A raw veal sirloin.

label: veal shoulder
definition: A veal primal cut that is the upper foreleg extending from elbow to blade bone.

label: veal shoulder (raw)
definition: A raw veal shoulder.

label: veal shoulder blade
definition: A veal meat cut in which the cut location is the full length of the Scapula or blade bone and includes the muscle groups above and below the Scapula.
comment: Requires discussion

label: veal shoulder blade (raw)
definition: A raw veal shoulder arm cut.

label: veal shoulder arm
definition: A veal meat cut in which shoulder arm consists of the muscle groups that extend from the elbow joint to the shoulder joint and includes the first three ribs.
comment: Requires discussion

label: veal shoulder arm (raw)
definition: A raw veal shoulder blade cut.

label: emu fan fillet
definition: A butchery cut from the inner thigh.

label: emu fan fillet (raw)
definition: A raw emu fan fillet.

label: emu flat fillet
definition: A butchery cut from thigh.

label: emu flat fillet (raw)
definition: A raw emu flat fillet.

label: emu full rump
definition: A butchery cut from emu.

label: emu full rump (raw)
definition: A raw emu full rump.

label: emu inside drum
definition: A butchery cut from emu.

label: emu inside drum (raw)
definition: A raw emu inside drum.

label: emu outside drum
definition: A butchery cut from emu.

label: emu outside drum (raw)
definition: A raw emu outside drum.

label: emu oyster
definition: An oyster from an emu.

label: emu oyster (raw)
definition: A raw emu oyster.

label: ostrich fan fillet
definition: A boneless fan shaped muscle (iliofibularis) that lies medially to the outside thigh

label: ostrich fan fillet (raw)
definition: A raw ostrich fan fillet.

label: ostrich inside leg
definition: A boneless cut derived from the leg.

label: ostrich inside leg (raw)
definition: A raw ostrich inside leg.

label: ostrich oyster
definition: An oyster from an Ostrich that is a flat, oval shaped muscle which lies anteriorly and dorsally to the outside thigh and is that portion of the thigh which attaches to the anterior end of the ilium.

label: ostrich oyster (raw)
definition: A raw ostrich oyster.

label: ostrich outside leg
definition: A boneless cut from the outside portion of the leg.

label: ostrich outside leg (raw)
definition: A raw ostrich outside leg.

label: ostrich inside strip
definition: A butchery cut from an ostrich that lies below the outside thigh and fan and covers the ilium of the carcass.

label: ostrich inside strip (raw)
definition: A raw ostrich inside strip cut.

label: ostrich outside strip
definition: A butchery cut from an ostrich that is pointed at one end and semi-circled shaped on the other. On the carcass this cut attaches to the posterior end of the ischium of the pelvis and anteriorly to the stifle joint.

label: ostrich outside strip (raw)
definition: A raw ostrich outside strip cut.

label: ostrich tip
definition: A butchery cut from an ostrich that is a "small ball" appearing muscle complex of the thigh and lies anteriorly, medially, and laterally to the stifle joint.

label: ostrich tip (raw)
definition: A raw ostrich tip cut.

label: ostrich outside thigh
definition: A boneless cut which is the largest major outside muscle system of the thigh and lies to the outside (laterally) of the fan.

label: ostrich outside thigh (raw)
definition: A raw ostrich outside thigh.

label: ostrich top strip
definition: A meat cut that is the rectangular shaped muscle (iliotibialis cranialis) and is the most anterior muscle in the thigh.

label: ostrich top strip (raw)
definition: A raw ostrich top strip cut.

label: ostrich tenderloin (raw)
definition: A raw ostrich tenderloin.

label: elk eye of round roast
definition: A cut of meat that is found between the top and bottom round roast located on both hindquarters of the elk.

label: elk eye of round roast (raw)
Equivalence axiom: 'elk eye of round roast' and 'has quality' some 'raw'
definition: A raw elk eye of round roast.

label: bison sirloin
definition: A bison primal cut that is contained within the larger cut 'bison loin'. It is located between the short loin and the round and includes the hip section and ends at the socket of the pelvis.
comment: Further separated into the Top and Bottom Sirloin Butt.

label: bison sirloin (raw)
definition: A raw bison sirloin cut.

label: bison top sirloin butt
definition: A bison cut that is located behind the short loin on the top back end of the animal.
comment: The name originates from its anatomical location on the “Top” (dorsal) of the Sirloin.

label: bison top sirloin butt (raw)
Equivalence axiom: 'bison top sirloin butt' and 'has quality' some 'raw'
definition: A raw bison top sirloin butt.

label: bison retail cut
definition: A bison meat cut that is derived from a sub-primal, individual muscle cut or minor primal cut.

label: bison steak
definition: A bison meat cut that has a flat-cut appearance.

label: bison top sirloin steak
Equivalence axiom: 'bison steak' and 'derives from' some 'bison top sirloin butt'
definition: A steak cut from the bison top sirloin butt.
comment: The name originates from its anatomical location on the “Top” (dorsal) of the Sirloin.

label: bison top sirloin steak (raw)
definition: A raw bison top sirloin steak.

label: bison round
definition: A bison cut that comes from the 'round', the rear leg of the bison.
comment: Sometimes referred to as the “bison Hip.”

label: bison round (raw)
definition: A raw bison round cut.

label: bison top round
definition: A bison cut that comes from the inside of the rear leg.
comment: Given the name “Top” because anatomically it is located directly above the Bottom Round and the Eye of Round in the Round primal.

label: bison top round (raw)
definition: A raw bison top round cut.

label: bison top round steak
Equivalence axiom: 'bison steak' and 'derives from' some 'bison top round'
definition: A steak cut from the bison top round.

label: bison top round steak (raw)
Equivalence axiom: 'bison top round steak' and 'has quality' some 'raw'
definition: A raw bison top round steak.

label: bison ribeye steak
definition: A bison steak that is a cut from the rib-eye roast.

label: bison ribeye steak (raw)
definition: A raw bison ribeye steak.

label: bison chuck
definition: A bison cut that extends from the neck to the fifth rib and includes the shoulder blade and upper arm.

label: bison chuck (raw)
definition: A raw bison chuck cut.

label: bison shoulder clod
definition: A large muscle system which lies dorsal and posterior to the elbow joint, ventral and posterior to the ridge of the scapula (blade bone) and is anterior to the 6th rib.
comment: Centred around the scapula or blade bone in the Chuck. Scapula is removed to make this a boneless subprimal.

label: bison shoulder clod (raw)
definition: A raw bison shoulder clod.

label: buffalo round
definition: A buffalo cut that comes from the 'round', the rear leg of the buffalo.
comment: Sometimes referred to as the “buffalo Hip.”

label: buffalo round (raw)
definition: A raw buffalo round cut.

label: buffalo top round
definition: A buffalo cut that comes from the inside of the rear leg.
comment: Given the name “Top” because anatomically it is located directly above the Bottom Round and the Eye of Round in the Round primal.

label: buffalo top round (raw)
definition: A raw buffalo top round cut.

label: buffalo retail cut
definition: A buffalo meat cut that is derived from a sub-primal, individual muscle cut or minor primal cut.

label: buffalo steak
definition: A buffalo meat cut that has a flat-cut appearance.

label: buffalo top round steak
Equivalence axiom: 'buffalo steak' and 'derives from' some 'buffalo top round'
definition: A steak cut from the buffalo top round.

label: buffalo top round steak (raw)
Equivalence axiom: 'buffalo top round steak' and 'has quality' some 'raw'
definition: A raw buffalo top round steak.
